025c4ced6fb2d78f","tid":2157501,"uid":272422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T07:04:45.000Z","msg":"本多終勝"},{"pid":"a4590ecaf6ca1f36b758539115d9cf724373826d","tid":2157501,"uid":251366,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T07:06:07.000Z","msg":"- 賺要有膽坐 蝕要果斷止蝕<br />\n- 簡單而言要順勢而行 跟市場方向 搵而家熱門既板塊<br />\n- 唔做第一個入場 亦都唔做最後一個入場<br />\n- 學識睇圖 就會知道邊啲位係買入點同賣出點 因為大部份人同埋電腦盤都係跟圖做trade<br />\n- 唔好玩你唔了解嗰行既股票 買之前確認下短線有冇利好消息 長線前景好唔好<br />\n- 分散投資 好多你預計唔到既事 要避免allin落一隻股票或者一個行業入面<br />\n- 唔買槓桿産品 唔好急進 股票係長遠投資 唔係一秒鐘既賭博<br />\n- 永遠保持平靜心境 賺唔好太高興 蝕唔好灰心 要有心理準備呢刻賺 下一刻會蝕返"},{"pid":"06927d2c7b46e4e8da728c54e7d769c6320ab864","tid":2157501,"uid":356101,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"e190fd3354397a4931b527c6979a6fbe9c8c968c","tid":2157501,"uid":14605,"like":45,"dislike":1,"score":44,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T05:36:49.000Z","msg":"唔好上咁多財經台，撚新手多"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T07:06:50.000Z","msg":"千萬唔好聽連登仔講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n中學生扮股神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68929dc5066a5b8eb3f54fbf83843d59b7469538","tid":2157501,"uid":234414,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T07:10:08.000Z","msg":"定止蝕<br />\n<br />\n又係呢啲 <br />\n<br />\n10000輸10%  =9000<br />\n下次9000賺10% =9900<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n10000輸50%=5000<br />\n下次5000要賺100%  先回本"},{"pid":"e78f15c073592b819cfee30c06baedb431824dd5","tid":2157501,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T07:10:55.000Z","msg":"蕭生預準 一定要知係點解讀<br />\n<br />\n唔係衰硬"},{"pid":"4e5d187a217c45850f6d873e22347186aeb4305c","tid":2157501,"uid":20164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T07:11:09.000Z","msg":"一定要學識高買低賣"},{"pid":"0d0372d9fdd60e2d55ae53937999cd7a03b06ea